data.description: Welcome to this Pinterest-Perfect Farmhouse style home located in Winder Ga! Boasting 4 bed room 2 full bath in main house PLUS 1 bedroom 1 full bath , separate laundry room , living room and kitchen in Guest house. Guest house also has an attached work shop large enough for 2 vehicles plus a working station. Entire home has been brought current with all major components being replaced in the last 4 years including Roof, HVAC and Water heater for both dwellings. Located just off Atlanta highway minuets from Athens Ga. No neighborhood, No HOA. . No access for guesthouse will be granted until contract is secured. Tenant in place for $800 per month but on Month to Month lease and will move out upon sale of property.
